{"tid":1575920,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"今日黨鐵脫軌單野，唔係意外，係企圖謀殺！","createTime":"2019-09-17T04:23:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T04:49:15.000Z","uid":254292,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d75eef5d16b6da88f1df78efddc01e507d149b59","tid":1575920,"uid":254292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T04:23:52.000Z","msg":"今日黨鐵脫軌單野冇人死，，得幾個輕傷，呢個先至係「意外」，意料之外。<br />\n<br />\n好簡單咁睇返，2010年打後，每一單世界各地既列車脫軌事故，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係幾乎每一單都有人死，重傷既更加不計其數。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔信既話，自己睇：<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/鐵路事故列表#2010年代\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E9%90%B5%E8%B7%AF%E4%BA%8B%E6%95%85%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8%232010%E5%B9%B4%E4%BB%A3&d=CoEtBkFB9dbfLkjoGL86rT4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=ecd9d432\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/鐵路事故列表#2010年代</a><br />\n<br />\n眾所周知，黨鐵事故率近幾年爆升，至於咩原因，一句 Made in China，大家心照。<br />\n<br />\n呢次係一個末世警號，下一劑一定死傷慘重。<br />\n<br />\n一定要將件事，推比啲剩係識返工既人，因為由呢次事件開始，再唔調查黨鐵既話、再唔去問責黨鐵既話，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你搭得黨鐵，就預左會死。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n呢件事一定要煲大佢，唔可以又比佢則則膊、吳多閣！"},{"pid":"de1eaa5c2782a27f422cde0e1474efd5802cb155","tid":1575920,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T04:25:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yt2HG33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyt2HG33.jpg&h=9fcb0aae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TrPZKfU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTrPZKfU.jpg&h=433e1fe6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f01ba22ac4846d99679b2beaa1c6189220e23889","tid":1575920,"uid":254292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T04:49:15.000Z","msg":"自推"}]}